in oue blog

Features
=============
Blog will have the following features

1. Post (Table in database)
2. Categories (Table in database)
3. Tag (Table in database)
4. Author (Table in database)

Relationships between our tables
====================================

1. Post can have many categories and a category can have many posts
   (Relationship between Post and Category Table)  (ManyToMany Relation)
2. A tag can have many post and a post can have many tah (ManyToMany relation)
3. Author can have many posts and a post can have a sigle author (OneToMany relation)
   [no post can be written by more than one author]

Attributes for tables
=======================

Post
====
 title
1.
2.created_date
3. body
4. tags
5. Categories
6. Author

Categories
============

1. cat_name
2. cat_description

Author
========

1. Author name
2. Author email (not mandatory)
3. Author bio

Tag
====

1. tag_name